      <div class="box">
        <p class="box-label">ON CAMPUS/STUDENTS</p>
        <div class="box-inner">
          <img src="/assets/photo/12.png">
          Each article must have at least one relevant feature photo and one in-text photo. The more the merrier!
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
